                    <span>I bought this book after reading about it in my yoga magazine thinking I could really use a good book of poems to ponder and this book is terrific.  The poems really will quiet your mind.  I love that such a wide array of authors are represented - from Rumi to Dogen to Emily Dickenson to Walt Whitman.  A great collection. Glad I bought it.</span>
                  
