                    <span>One of the most inspiring collections or sacred poetry ever compiled. The translations are perfect. The sensual/spiritual quality of the words can transport you into altered states. Beautiful. Al Link - 4 Freedoms Tantra</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Poetry of spirit throughout the ages - delightful reading</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
